Package: HrdDetective
Type: Package
Title: Detect HRD in Human Cancer Cells
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Meng Li
Maintainer: Meng Li <limeng49631@aliyun.com>
Description: This package implements an algorithm based on PELT algorithm and Sequenza statistical model for detecting HRD (Homologous Recombination Deficiency) in human cancer cells.
